items.headline: Learn more about the Samurai Champloo Wikia
items.desc: The Samurai Champloo Wikia community is a fan site dedicated to being the number one resourcein everything related to  the anime Samurai Champloo. The format allows anyone to edit or create any article and is kept up-to-date by editors like you so that Samurai Champloo Wikia becomes the largest database on Samurai Champloo. Become a member and you can help us expand Samurai Champloo, so it may grow.
